body:
I mean really- You&#039;d think at some point someone at Riot would lose a promo series or get demoted because someone on their team disconnects, and think, &quot;Hmm, shouldn&#039;t we have a system that prevents loss penalties whenever there is a disconnected player on the team?&quot;

I was just demoted in a game where I got off to a good start, yet my JG disconnected at level 3 and we ended up losing, slowly (because we should have won the game). I mean COME ON, this game is over 6 years old and you still haven&#039;t come up with a system that says, &quot;Hey, this player spent 70% of the game time sitting in the fountain. Maybe his teammates shouldn&#039;t be demoted.&quot; 

But no. Lose game to DC on your team, get demoted. someone on my team was also in their series. THIS IS SO FRUSTRATING
